	(text_box "Divider formula: VADC = VSW * RLOW / (RHIGH + RLOW). Example with RHIGH = 100k and RLOW = 33k: VADC = VSW * 33k / 133k = VSW * 0.248, so 10.8 V on +VSW becomes about 2.68 V at the STM32 ADC.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 92.71 20.32 0)
		(size 45.72 15.24)
